    "Remain read-only and replay all 77 staged-blob hashes plus the aggregate before review.",
    "Review the complete subject and both final-review remediations, prioritizing whether the real-lock test now proves no completion/no mutation during contention and byte-distinct recheck-before-write preservation after unlock.",
    "Confirm the deliberate lock-bypass and write-before-recheck mutation evidence is sufficient, production bytes remain unchanged, and the prior implementation/smoke/validator proof remains sound.",
    "Return findings first with exact file/line evidence and the smallest in-scope remediation."
  ],
  "non_goals": [
    "No edits, staging, commits, handoff/ledger writes, or user task hops.",
    "No HCM-2.2+, definition/schema/Cargo/pipeline/stage/installed-skill/SDK changes or adjacent cleanup.",
    "No reuse of either earlier final reviewer; this review requires another different fresh isolated reviewer."
  ],
