    "Admit the exact canonical-LF manifest and review the complete implementation, security, authority, regression, and proof subject.",
    "Verify the byte-distinct lock/recheck regression is mutation-sensitive to both missing-lock and write-before-recheck defects while untouched production remains green.",
    "Return CLEAN only with no Critical or Required finding; otherwise CHANGES_REQUIRED or BLOCKED."
